title: Beautiful 3br 21/2 bath
posting_body: Beautiful 3 br , 21/2 bath home in very desirable Harbor Town ,close to famous Pyramid (Pro Bass )Bldg ,U.T; St Jude Hospital , Famous Beale Street and play area and a famous River Walk on The Mighty Mississippi River.

The kitchen has been renovated with granite counter top and new appliances along ,new vinyl flooring on the entire Ist floor ,new carpet on the second floor and comes with all the appliances including Refrigerator ,Washer/Dryer ,Dish Washer, Stove Top ,Oven and Microwave!
